<p>Then she sparked dating rumors after she and Delevingne, 28, were spotted affectionately embracing at a Black Lives Matter rally in July.</p>

<p>They also got matching 'Solemate' tattoos on their feet in August. </p>

<p>However, a source told E! that the teen beauty is happy playing the field right now as she focuses on her career. </p>

<p>'Kaia is the one that doesn't want to be in an exclusive relationship right now. She has a lot of projects on her plate and wants her freedom,' the source said.</p>

